title: Wednesday’s prep tennis results
text:
Redmond 5, Woodinville 2 Singles —Max Wing, W, def. Nokolay Bykov, R, 6-2, 6-4; Eric Yang, W, def. Aaron Ong, R, 6-1, 7-6; Van Kim, R, def. Cole Stafford, W, 6-2, 4-6, 6-3; Noah Yeo, R, def. Tyler Borgeson, W, 7-6, 6-3.
Doubles —Ethan Raffman-Adarsh Karnati, R, def. Christian Brisbois-Esh Sathiyamoorthy, W, 6-4, 6-3; Peter Nikolic-Keenan Ganz, R, def. Drew Campton-Rand Mattis, W, 6-4, 6-2; Richard Zhang-Dalai Chadraa, R, def. Duncan Long-Simon Day, W, 7-6, 6-1.
Auburn 3, Auburn Mountainview 2 Singles —Bryan Thornquist, A, def. Rylee Daugherty, AM, 6-0, 6-0; Troy Preshun, A, def. Andre Hall, AM, 6-0, 6-0.
Doubles —Garrett Neiss-Billy Boraphet, AM, def. Michael Spray-Mason Ruffin, A, 7-5, 4-6, 10-7; Hans Thorbjornsen-Juan Hayes-Gonzalez, AM, def. Ryan Yorke-Kendrick Smythe, A, 6-2, 6-2; Mason McInerny-Paul Onishenko, A, def. Adam Rhoades-Ben Portmann, AM, 6-3, 6-1.
